@startuml
' @id(SEQ-MAP-SCOPE)
' @ref(USE-SCOPED-REMAP)
' @desc(SEQ-MAP-SCOPE, "Project::map_scope(N, base): build model_registry + read_trace + cycle_registry; manifest = cycle(N).manifest. REVERSE: changed = traceability::changed_code(root, base); changed_files = union of symbol.path + glue.path; for each file, links = source_links with l.path == file; if empty -> scope_escapes.insert(file); else for each link insert current_file_for(link.model_id) into affected. FORWARD: for each manifest.scope id, insert current_file_for(id), else the objective file's mirror current path. full_remap = !scope_escapes.is_empty(). Return MapScopePlan. The /mdd-cycle loop runs the verb each iteration and hands affected_files (or whole-tree on full_remap) to /mdd-map; /mdd-validate then runs whole-tree.")
title Scoped re-map — map-scope plan (current)

participant "/mdd-cycle loop\n(CMP-CYCLE-ORCHESTRATOR)" as Cycle
participant "mdd map-scope\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-CLI)" as Cli
participant "Project::map_scope()\n(CMP-MAP-SCOPE-ENGINE)" as Engine
participant "CycleRegistry\nmanifest" as Manifest
participant "trace.yml\nsource_links" as Trace
participant "changed_code\n(CMP-TRACE-ENGINE)" as Changed
participant "MapScopePlan" as Plan
participant "/mdd-map" as Map

Cycle -> Cli : map-scope --cycle N --json
Cli -> Engine : map_scope(N, base)
Engine -> Manifest : cycle(N).manifest (scope)
Engine -> Changed : changed_code(root, base)
Changed --> Engine : changed source files

loop each changed source file
  Engine -> Trace : source_links where path matches
  alt at least one matches
    Trace --> Engine : (model_id, path)*
    Engine -> Plan : insert current diagram file(s)
  else none
    Engine -> Plan : push scope_escape (forces full_remap)
  end
end

loop each scope @id in manifest
  Engine -> Plan : insert current-side concept file
end

Plan --> Engine : { cycle, affected_files, scope_escapes, full_remap }
Engine --> Cli : MapScopePlan
Cli --> Cycle : JSON plan

alt full_remap
  Cycle -> Map : re-derive whole current/ tree
else narrowed
  Cycle -> Map : re-derive only affected_files
end
@enduml
